<div id="ta3_85" class="block iDevice_content">
<p style="color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">La clasificación según las<span> </span><b style="color: #000000 !important; font-weight: bold !important; display: inline !important;">necesidades</b>, indica la existencia de dos grupos:</p>
<p style="color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"></p>
<div class="elementInteractive" style="margin: 0pt; padding: 20px; clear: both; position: relative; color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; border: 1px dashed #008ed1;">
<div class="iconoInteractive" style="background: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/imagenes/CSS000016/icono_interactivo.png') center center no-repeat scroll transparent; left: -21px; top: -20px; height: 40px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; right: 40px; width: 40px; position: absolute;"></div>
<div id="accordion" class="accordion ui-accordion ui-widget ui-helper-reset ui-accordion-icons" role="tablist" style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.3; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1em; list-style: none; width: 239.391px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible;">
<h3 class="ui-accordion-header ui-helper-reset ui-state-default ui-state-active ui-corner-top" role="tab" aria-expanded="true" aria-selected="true" style="margin: 1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid #79b7e7; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.3; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; list-style: none; background: url('images/ui-bg_inset-hard_100_f5f8f9_1x100.png') 50% 50% repeat-x #f5f8f9; font-weight: bold; color: #3f598c; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; text-align: justify; cursor: pointer; position: relative; zoom: 1;" tabindex="0"><span class="ui-icon ui-icon-triangle-1-s" style="display: block; text-indent: -99999px; overflow: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-image: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/jqueryUI/images/ui-icons_6da8d5_256x240.png'); background-position: -64px -16px; position: absolute; left: 0.5em; top: 22.3906px; margin-top: -8px;"></span><a href="http://www.rpcformacion.es/cursosonline/pluginfile.php/5444/mod_scorm/content/1/cargador.html?r=VVQ5dUxuJTJGbkZCUnNzMVZNOVVmbHd3MnNUSjhLM2JEMmdlUW1LTEtROTFuTXNhS1pqbThkeEVUUzRGT0ZQU3p6TEF2cjBOdXZ4ZW1vOTNRNWExdyUyRktBJTNEJTNE&amp;p=TDBTWGJDdDFZUHVHNVN0QSUyQlNhVnR4RDFUTUh1VEZ1WXNUd2FINWJIaXJzJTNE&amp;v=HTM_cyUyQm1lUDM0aUE0RWc2dHBpJTJGJTJCNWhFelplUk9uazhnR1lmcnZxWVZwNzRHZyUzRA==&amp;c=SUxVamxkbzUlMkJuUmpocUVGWTdLR0VaR3JjcDVjR3BuUkZuJTJCJTJCYktXeWdKUSUzRA==&amp;t=2.%20Clasificaci%C3%B3n#section1" style="color: #2e6e9e; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8em; display: block; padding: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 2.2em; vertical-align: middle;">1.<span> </span>Micronutrientes mayoritarios</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content ui-helper-reset ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom ui-accordion-content-active" role="tabpanel" style="margin: -2px 0px 2px; padding: 1em 2.2em; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.3; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; list-style: none; background: url('images/ui-bg_inset-hard_100_fcfdfd_1x100.png') 50% bottom repeat-x #fcfdfd; color: #222222; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; position: relative; top: 1px; overflow: auto; display: block; zoom: 1; border-color: initial #a6c9e2 #a6c9e2 #a6c9e2; border-style: initial solid solid solid;">Son aquellos minerales que necesitamos en cantidades de 100mg/día o más y forman más del 0,005% del peso corporal. Son el sodio, potasio, calcio, fósforo, magnesio, cloro y azufre.</div>
<h3 class="ui-accordion-header ui-helper-reset ui-state-default ui-corner-all" role="tab" aria-expanded="false" aria-selected="false" style="margin: 1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid #c5dbec; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.3; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; list-style: none; background: url('images/ui-bg_glass_85_dfeffc_1x400.png') 50% 50% repeat-x #dfeffc; font-weight: bold; color: #3f598c; border-radius: 5px; text-align: justify; cursor: pointer; position: relative; zoom: 1;" tabindex="-1"><span class="ui-icon ui-icon-triangle-1-e" style="display: block; text-indent: -99999px; overflow: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-image: url('images/ui-icons_6da8d5_256x240.png'); background-position: -32px -16px; position: absolute; left: 0.5em; top: 38.3906px; margin-top: -8px;"></span><a href="http://www.rpcformacion.es/cursosonline/pluginfile.php/5444/mod_scorm/content/1/cargador.html?r=VVQ5dUxuJTJGbkZCUnNzMVZNOVVmbHd3MnNUSjhLM2JEMmdlUW1LTEtROTFuTXNhS1pqbThkeEVUUzRGT0ZQU3p6TEF2cjBOdXZ4ZW1vOTNRNWExdyUyRktBJTNEJTNE&amp;p=TDBTWGJDdDFZUHVHNVN0QSUyQlNhVnR4RDFUTUh1VEZ1WXNUd2FINWJIaXJzJTNE&amp;v=HTM_cyUyQm1lUDM0aUE0RWc2dHBpJTJGJTJCNWhFelplUk9uazhnR1lmcnZxWVZwNzRHZyUzRA==&amp;c=SUxVamxkbzUlMkJuUmpocUVGWTdLR0VaR3JjcDVjR3BuUkZuJTJCJTJCYktXeWdKUSUzRA==&amp;t=2.%20Clasificaci%C3%B3n#section1" style="color: #4b8fc7; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8em; display: block; padding: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 2.2em; vertical-align: middle;">2.<span> </span>Micronutrientes minoritarios, oligoelementos o elementos traza</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<p style="color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"></p>
<p style="color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Según su<span> </span><b style="color: #000000 !important; font-weight: bold !important; display: inline !important;">función</b>, los minerales se clasifican en:</p>
<ul style="color: #202020; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 15px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">
<li style="list-style-image: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/imagenes/CSS000013/li.png'); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; opacity: 1 !important;">Plásticos: calcio, fósforo, magnesio y flúor.</li>
<li style="list-style-image: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/imagenes/CSS000013/li.png'); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; opacity: 1 !important;">Electrolitos: sodio, potasio, cloruros y fosfatos.</li>
<li style="list-style-image: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/imagenes/CSS000013/li.png'); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; opacity: 1 !important;">Componentes de moléculas orgánicas complejas: hierro (forma parte de la hemoglobina), yodo (de las hormonas tiroideas), cobalto (de la vitamina B12).</li>
<li style="list-style-image: url('//www.educalms.com/REPOSITORIO/CSS/CSS000500/imagenes/CSS000013/li.png'); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; opacity: 1 !important;">Elementos traza: cinc, cobre, selenio…actúan como metaloenzimas o cofactores.</li>
</ul>
